quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,"M wẽen ne sebdã sẽn fugdã."
  77,2,"La ne sob-kugdsã kugb tεkẽ."
  77,3,"La ne sob-fãeeds fãeegr tεkẽ."
  77,4,"La M wẽen ne Mɑlεk-rãmb nins sẽn sigd ne sẽn wεlgd sɩd lɑ zĩri sʋkã."
  77,5,"La ne Mɑlεk-rãmb nins sẽn sigd ne wɑhɩ wã n leemsd aaya-rãmbã."
  77,6,"Padmes yĩng ma bugsg yĩnga."
  77,7,"Bũmb ning b sẽn pʋlem yãmbã na n yɩɩme."
  77,8,"La ãdsã sã n wa yẽese."
  77,9,"La saagã sã n wa pãrse."
  77,10,"La tãmsã sã n wa vigsi."
  77,11,"La tẽn-tʋʋmbã sã n wa ta b wakatã tɩ b tigim-bɑ."
  77,12,"La rabʋr yĩng la b yaoond yεla?"
  77,13,"Yaa welgrã raar yĩnga."
  77,14,"La bõe n wilgd foo welgr raar sẽn yaa a soaba?"
  77,15,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,16,"Rẽ yĩngã Tõnd pa halk reng taoor rãmbã,"
  77,17,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ d pʋglg bãmb neb a taabã?"
  77,18,"Woto bal la D tʋm ne nin-wẽnsã."
  77,19,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,20,"Rẽ yĩnga D pa naan yãmb n yi ko-yaalga,"
  77,21,"Tɩ D ning-a tabendg zĩig sẽn tar gũubu."
  77,22,"N tʋg wakat b sẽn mi."
  77,23,"Tɩ Tõnd kord-ɑ nɑɑnegã, ad Tõnd kordg be neere."
  77,24,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,25,"Tõnd pa maan tẽngã tɩ yaa kʋmbda,"
  77,26,"Vɩtbã la kiidbã,"
  77,27,"La D ning a pʋgẽ tãens sẽn lugi, la D yũnug yãmb koom sẽn noome?"
  77,28,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,29,"Kẽng-y n tʋg bũmb ning y sẽn da yagsdã."
  77,30,"Kẽng-y n tʋg maasem sẽn yaa buk a tãabo (gεhanm bug zõosẽ wã)."
  77,31,"Ka maasem, a pa gɩdgd bug-vilingã me tɩ pɑ tɑ-yã."
  77,32,"Ad a fãeeda bug-pãrs sẽn yaa wala gãsdo,"
  77,33,"A yaa wala yʋgm sɑblɑ."
  77,34,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,35,"Yãoã yaa raar b sẽn pa gomde."
  77,36,"La b pa kõt-b sor me tɩ b padem ye."
  77,37,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,38,"Yãoã yaa welgrã raare, Tõnd tigma yãmb la rẽenem rãmba."
  77,39,"Y sã n tara rabr bɩ y rabs-ma."
  77,40,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,41,"Ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee maasem pʋgẽ la ko-ninẽ."
  77,42,"La tɩ-biisẽ bãmb sẽn nong a soaba."
  77,43,"Rɩ-y la y yũ, yaa beelg ne yãmb y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã sɑbɑb."
  77,44,"Ad yaa woto la Tõnd keood manegdbã."
  77,45,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,46,"Rɩ-y-yã la y wʋmsd noog bilfu bala, ad yãmb yaa nin-wẽnse."
  77,47,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩrimbe-rãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,48,"B sã n yeel-b tɩ b maan rukuu, b pa maand ye."
  77,49,"Wɩɩbd be ne zĩri-bemrãmbã ra-kãng raare."
  77,50,"La yaa gomd bʋg la b kõt sɩda a (Alkʋrãanã) loogr poorẽ, ( tɩ y sã n pɑ kõ-sɩd ne Kɑrãɑnã)?"
